Sure, here are a few up-and-coming country artists worth checking out:

1. Morgan Wallen - He has been making waves in country music with his unique blend of traditional country and modern pop sounds.

2. Ingrid Andress - She is a talented songwriter and vocalist with a fresh sound and honest, relatable lyrics.

3. Kacey Musgraves - She has gained popularity in recent years with her bold and genre-defying approach to country music.

4. Luke Combs - He has quickly become one of the biggest names in country music with his powerful voice and catchy, introspective songs.

5. Tenille Townes - She is a rising star in the country music scene with a soulful voice, authentic lyrics, and a positive message.

These are just a few examples of the many talented country artists out there right now. Hopefully, you find some music that you enjoy!
